title: Best Receiver Draft Picks in the Last 10 Years | Big Board
description:
The Ringer Fantasy Football Show's Danny Heifetz and Danny Kelly discuss the 10 best-value wide receiver draft picks in the last 10 years. Then they go through some receivers from this year's draft class who could be the next midround gems.

Follow ‘The Ringer Fantasy Football Show.’

Check out The Ringer Draft Guide.

Hosts: Danny Heifetz and Danny Kelly
